ndwiches, and snacks at various locations in and around Zurich.','Les meilleurs produits de boulangerie, sandwichs et tartes Wähen à Zurich et aux alentours. ','Prodotti da forno di qualità, sandwich e torte presso diverse filiali di Zurigo e dintorni.',NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_baeckerei-wuest_01.jpg','2020-02-18 19:23:01 +0100','Patisserie','Patisserie','Réservation cours de pâtisserie',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_baeckerei-wuest_05.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
