ndwiches, and snacks at various locations in and around Zurich.','Les meilleurs produits de boulangerie, sandwichs et tartes Wähen à Zurich et aux alentours. ','Prodotti da forno di qualità, sandwich e torte presso diverse filiali di Zurigo e dintorni.',NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_baeckerei-wuest_01.jpg','2020-02-18 19:23:01 +0100','Patisserie','Patisserie','Pâtisserie','Pasticceria','CH','Zürich',8006,'Stampfenbachstrasse 30','info@bywuest.ch','www.baeckereiwuest.ch',47.379100800000,8.543677900000,'<p>Montag bis Freitag, 06.30 &ndash; 18.00 Uhr<br />Samstag bis Sonntag, 07.00 &ndash; 17.00 Uhr</p>','<p>Monday to Friday, 6.30am &ndash; 6.00pm<br />Saturday and Sunday, 7.00am &ndash; 5.00pm</p>','<p>Du lundi au vendredi, 6h30 &ndash; 18h<br />Du samedi au dimanche, 7h00 &ndash; 17h</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì, 06.30 &ndash; 18.00<br />Sabato e domenica, 07.00 &ndash; 17.00</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday,Sunday','POINT (47.3791008 8.5436779)',6,'+41 44 380 88 22',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/imagegallery/web_zurich_baeckerei-wuest_05.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),
