ario di un diner americano degli anni Cinquanta.&nbsp;</p>','Helvti Diner','Helvti Diner','Helvti Diner','Helvti Diner','Amerikanische-Diner-Atmosphäre mit Gourmet-Burgern in der Nähe vom Stauffacher.','US diner ambiance with gourmet burgers, near Stauffacher','Ambiance de « diner » américain avec des burgers gastronomiques près de l’arrêt de tram Stauffacher.','Atmosfera da diner americano con hamburger gourmet nei pressi dello Stauffacher.',4857867456,'https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_restaurant_helvtidiner_04.jpg','2020-04-06 17:06:34 +0200','50er-Jahre-Stil','1950s style','Style des années 50','Stile anni Cinquanta','CH','Zürich',8004,'Kasernenstrasse 2','office@helvti-diner.ch','www.helvti-diner.ch',47.373583300000,8.532033700000,'<p>Montag bis Freitag, 10.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr<br /><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Samstag 11.00 &ndash; 24.00 Uhr</span></p><p>Die Küche ist wochentags zwischen 14.30 &ndash; 18.00 Uhr geschlossen.</p>','<p>Monday to Friday, 10.00am &ndash; 12.00am<br /><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Saturday 11.00am &ndash; 12.00am</span></p><p>During the week, the kitchen is closed from 2.30 &ndash; 6.00pm.</p>','<p>Du lundi au vendredi, 10h &ndash;&nbsp;24h<br /><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Samedi 11h &ndash;&nbsp;24h</span></p><p>En semaine, la cuisine est fermée de 14h30 à 18h.</p>','<p>Da lunedì a venerdì, 10.00 &ndash;&nbsp;24.00<br /><span style="line-height: 1.5;">Sabato 11.00 &ndash;&nbsp;24.00</span></p><p>In settimana, la cucina è chiusa tra le 14.30 e le 18.00.</p>','Monday,Tuesday,Wednesday,Thursday,Friday,Saturday','POINT (47.3735833 8.532033699999999)',4,'+41 43 322 04 24','Innenansicht','Interior view','Vue de l''intérieur','Vista interna','https://cdn.zuerich.com/sites/default/files/keyvisual/web_zurich_restaurant_helvtidiner_04.jpg','Innenansicht','Interior view','Vue de l''intérieur','Vista interna'),
